  "remarks": "Positive Group PJSC is the holding company of a conglomerate that includes AO Pozitiv Teknolodzhiz. AO Pozitiv Teknolodzhiz operates in the Russian IT sector and holds a licence administered by the FSB Centre for Licensing, Certification, and Protection of State Secrets. Thus, Positive Group PJSC is the holding company of a conglomerate that includes an entity operating in the Russian IT sector and holding a licence administered by the FSB.",
